      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Three passes through each round. Five to seven taps per point.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Energy statement pair",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "attrs": {
          "quote": "I release the feeling that they should still be the strong one. I release it now. I release it now. I release it now.",
          "attribution": null
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "attrs": {
          "quote": "I allow myself to be the one who carries this now, without losing my own life. I allow it now. I allow it now. I allow it now.",
          "attribution": null
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Journal prompts",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Three prompts. Five minutes each against a timer. Write without editing.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "1. What changed in the relationship when the flow reversed?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Practically and emotionally. Write specifically.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "2. What feels right about being able to give back?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Don't skip this one even if the resentment is loud. There is usually something true here.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "3. What is one specific limit I need to set on what I can give, said calmly and clearly?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the limit. Write the sentence you would use. Then read it back.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "After the practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Have the conversation with your parent this month if you haven't had it yet. Use the sentence from prompt 3 as the line. Come back to this practice when the resentment or grief feels heavy again.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
